{
  "stem": "20848.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't want to stay in Lodz because Lodz was immediately annexed to Third Reich.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they wanted to go to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from Warsaw we're going to Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember that soon after my father left, my mother-- in December we left for Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very, very hard to get to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I must mention here that we had a lot of German clients in our shop, because Lodz had a lot of-- big German population.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when my mother saw that she couldn't get out of Lodz-- there was no transport to get us out of Lodz-- she went to one of her ex-customer, who was running a bus service.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she went-- I was with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's why I remember that incident-- she went up to him, and she begged him to let us go to her husband, you know, to Warsaw with me and my brother.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he kept saying he's got no more room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He's not going to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother went to the window, and she said-- it was up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "His offices were high up-- and she went to the window, and she said to him, well, if you're not going to let me go to my husband with my children, then I'm going to throw myself out and commit suicide right in front of your eyes.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, that must have probably frightened him or maybe, I don't know, maybe touched his conscience a little bit.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he let us go on one of his buses to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They created some kind of a border, which was, of course, never there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But they created some kind of a border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And on the borderline, they got us all down from the buses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were searched.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
